snippet.title: When a Desi Visits Singapore
snippet.description:
Singapore, saare desi parivaro ka family trip destination dekh aaye!

We saw - the Merlion, Singapore flyer, Marina bay sands hotel, skyline luge, checked out Changi airport, jewel changi, went on duck tours, slingshot, night safari, saw the beautiful gardens by the bay and Singapore super trees, flower dome and cloud forest. 

Use our code SLAYY10 on Headout to get 10% discount on all Singapore experiences - https://bit.ly/489gJrH

snippet.title: Family Dinner l Mummy ka Birthday | Take A Break
snippet.description:
Get ready for a hilarious ride with our latest comedy sketch, "Family Dinner"! In this uproarious video, we follow a middle-class family as they embark on a memorable journey to an upscale restaurant to celebrate Mom's birthday. Watch as they navigate the uncharted waters of fine dining, leading to a series of comical misadventures.

snippet.title: Recipe 795;: Thuruvathirai Arudra
snippet.description:
Arudra Darshan is a Tamil festival and this day is dedicated to Lord Shiva. Arudra Nakshatram, which is also known as Thiruvaathirai Nakshatram, during Maargazhi Masam is considered highly auspicious. On this day Arudra Nakshatra also coincides with Pournami.

On this day Nataraj form of Lord Shiva is worshipped during Arunodaya along with holy chanting from Vedas. Being dedicated to Nataraj form of Lord Shiva this day is also considered as the birthday of Lord Shiva. In rest of the India it is Maha Shivaratri which is considered as the birthday of Lord Shiva.

So on this special occasion sending across a video of the recipe that is usually done on Thiruvathirai. 

Kindly have a look at the  Ingredients and recipe ; 

#Ingredients

#Kali

Raw Rice - 1 cup
Moong Dal - 1 tsp
Jaggery - 2 cup
Water - 3 cup
Cardamom Powder - 1/2 tsp
Grated Coconut - 4 to 5 spoon
Ghee - 4 spoon & Cashew Nuts

#7Kaai_Kootu

Ash gourd
Pumpkin
Broad Beans
Carrot
Yam
Raw Banana
Sweet Potato
Toor Dal - 2 tbsp
Oil - 7 spoon
Coriander Seeds - 3 spoon
Gram dal - 3 tsp
Pepepr Seeds - 1/2 tsp
Fenugreek - 1/4 tsp
Dry Chilli - 15 nos
Grated Coconut - 1/2
Curry Leaves
Lima Beans
Asafoetida - 4 piece
Water - 1 cup
Salt - 1 tsp
Turmeric Powder - 1/2 tsp
Curry Leaves
Jaggery small piece
Boiled Toor Dal - 4 tbsp
Mustard Seeds - 1 tsp
Dry Chilli - 3 nos

Khumar Episode 10 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 23rd December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

snippet.description:
In this video I have showed how we celebrate Christmas Eve at my home in London.
Christmas is an annual festival commemorating the birth of Jesus Christ, observed primarily on December 25 as a religious and cultural celebration among billions of people around the world.A feast central to the liturgical year in Christianity, it follows the season of Advent (which begins four Sundays before) or the Nativity Fast, and initiates the season of Christmastide, which historically in the West lasts twelve days and culminates on Twelfth Night.Christmas Day is a public holiday in many countries,is celebrated religiously by a majority of Christians,as well as culturally by many non-Christians,and forms an integral part of the holiday season surrounding it.

Christmas is an annual festival commemorating the birth of Jesus Christ, observed primarily on December 25 as a religious and cultural celebration among billions of people around the world.A feast central to the liturgical year in Christianity, it follows the season of Advent (which begins four Sundays before) or the Nativity Fast, and initiates the season of Christmastide, which historically in the West lasts twelve days and culminates on Twelfth Night.Christmas Day is a public holiday in many countries,is celebrated religiously by a majority of Christians,as well as culturally by many non-Christians,and forms an integral part of the holiday season surrounding it.

snippet.title: DIVINE - 4.10 | Official Music Video
snippet.description:
Download & Stream: https://lnk.to/4.10

Crafted against the evocative backdrop of a sampled melody from the legendary Punjabi singer Laal Chand Yamla Jatt, this musical masterpiece vividly depicts DIVINE's innermost thoughts and emotions. Produced by the duo Zzorawar and Arsh Heer, the beats resonate with the hauntingly beautiful verses of Yamla Jatt's classic, 'Tere Ni Karara Mainu Puteya,Das Main Ki Pyar Wichon Kuhteya' which translates to 'Your promises cost me dearly, tell me what did I gain from love.' This sample threads through the rhythm, infusing the track with an emotional depth that perfectly aligns with DIVINE's lyrical narrative.

Audio Credits:

Written and Performed by: DIVINE, Lal Chand Yamla Jatt
Produced by: ZZORAWAR, Arsh Heer
Mixed & Mastered by: Hanish Taneja

Video Credits:

Directed & Edited by Joel D'souza (JD) 
Shot by - Navkaran Brar & Joel D'souza (JD)
Colorist - Tapasvi Asija

#DIVINE #GullyGang

snippet.description:

Khumar Episode 09 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 22nd December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:

The Nawab wants to go to Krishnanager and make a mockery of Gopal. Meanwhile, Maharaj and all the members of the court go to Montri's house for a feast but Gopal eats all the sweets. How will Montri react to this?


Show Name: Gopal Bhar
Episode No: 1013

#GopalBhar #sonyaath #‡¶ó‡ßã‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶≤‡¶≠‡¶∞ 

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Main ATAL Hoon - Trailer | Pankaj Tripathi | Ravi Jadhav | Vinod Bhanushali | 19 Jan 2024
snippet.description:
More than a poet. More than a statesman. More than a Prime Minister. Presenting the trailer of #MainATALHoon. 

Vinod Bhanushali presents, Main ATAL Hoon, a film on the extraordinary life of the leader you knew but the man you didn't, starring National Award winner Pankaj Tripathi. 

Directed by National Awardee Ravi Jadhav, and written by Rishi Virmani and Ravi Jadhav, "Main ATAL Hoon" presented by Bhanushali Studios Limited and Legend Studios, is produced by Vinod Bhanushali, Sandeep Singh, and Kamlesh Bhanushali.
The film releases on 19th January 2024 in cinemas near you. 


CREDITS:

Starring : Pankaj Tripathi
Director : Ravi Jadhav
Producers : Vinod Bhanushali, Sandeep Singh and Kamlesh Bhanushali
Co Producer - Bhavesh Bhanushali, Sam Khan

snippet.title: Why RICH people wants to look POOR | Strange secrets of RICH | GIGL
snippet.description:
Why RICH people wants to look POOR | Strange secrets of RICH | GIGL

In short hamne is video me human psychology ke 3 amazing concepts ke baare me seekha pehla concept tha:- 

‚ÄúSocial proof in tribes‚Äù yaani ki agar ek ameer insaan ke normal customers hai aur vo unhi ki tarah deekhega to relatibility ke principle ke according log us ke saath zaada connect karenge jis se trust create hoga aur finally sales badegi. Is par detal me ek book hai Dr robert cialidini ki jiska naam hai ‚Äúinfluence the psychology of persuasion‚Äù . jise aap chahe to gigl app me free me hindi me sun sakte hai. Iska link mein description aur first comment me de dunga.

Next concept tha ‚ÄúNormal life style and being part of tribe‚Äù jisme hamne aman goel ka case dekha ki kaise vo simple hi rehna chahte hai kyunki 1) unhe ye life style pasand hai 2) unke jo saath wale log hai vo bhi unhe usi tareeke se dekhe jaise vo apne startup ko bechne se pehle dikhte the.

Next concept hamne seekha ‚Äúmaslow pyramid‚Äù jo ki human needs ke baare me batata hai ki kayi ameer logo ko bilkul fark nhi padta ki aur log kya soch rahe hai ya unhe bhaut ache kapde pehnne hai kyunki vo self actualization wale stage me phunch chuka hai.

In short ‚Ä¶ do type ke ameer hai dono simple dress karne ki koshish kar rahe hai.. Ek apni sales badhana chahta hai aur ek khud ko apne kaam se express karna chahta hai.

I hope ye video aapko achi lagi nogi.

--------------------------------------------------------
All of Sodhi and Roshan's friends in the society get Kada Prasad, and they are invited to their anniversary celebration. snippet.title: Visiting the Closest Town to Space (Life with 50% less oxygen)
snippet.description:
Subscribe ‚ñ∫ https://goo.gl/MKi8tn
La Rinconada, the closest inhabited place to the sky on Earth, where people are living above the clouds.

At this extreme altitude of 5,100 meters, the atmosphere significantly thins and the locals are living with only  50% of the usual oxygen levels. Their bodies have evolved to produce two times more blood cells than ours. On this barren land, not even a single tree can survive because of the low air pressure. 

This town in the Peruvian Andes is even 300 meters higher than Mont Blanc, the highest peak in the Alps of Europe. 
 
Far from the modern world, it is a place where crime and danger are always nearby.  People come to these harsh lands for only one reason: gold. About 50,000 people have settled here, among piles of trash, all dreaming of wealth.

""Rediscovery"" Series ‚ñ∫ https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL40Eh9f0PRRXcCkyKxrtRvE3tbmcKYvHr

en.title: Visiting the Closest Town to Space (Life with 50% less oxygen)
en.description:
Subscribe ‚ñ∫ https://goo.gl/MKi8tn
La Rinconada, the closest inhabited place to the sky on Earth, where people are living above the clouds.

At this extreme altitude of 5,100 meters, the atmosphere significantly thins and the locals are living with only  50% of the usual oxygen levels. Their bodies have evolved to produce two times more blood cells than ours. On this barren land, not even a single tree can survive because of the low air pressure. 

This town in the Peruvian Andes is even 300 meters higher than Mont Blanc, the highest peak in the Alps of Europe. 
 
Far from the modern world, it is a place where crime and danger are always nearby.  People come to these harsh lands for only one reason: gold. About 50,000 people have settled here, among piles of trash, all dreaming of wealth.

Lontano dal mondo moderno, √® un luogo dove la criminalit√† e il pericolo sono sempre vicini. Le persone vengono in queste terre aspre per una sola ragione: l'oro. Qui, tra cumuli di spazzatura, si sono stabilite circa 50.000 persone, tutte sognanti la ricchezza.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:

(Team at Studio Alika -  Ashish Ratani, Niranjan Sarbi, Akshay Moolya)

LYRICS

BADAL
YE TOH YAAD H NA YA LAAU LYRICS BHAI
MAI JITNA MEHNGA UTNA FREE TUMHARA FREESTYLE
PURE GAANO ME BAS YAAD EK HI CHEEZ
MERI JAAN MERI JAAN KUCH AAGE BHI TOH LIKH BHAI

POET SHAF 
MAINE JAAN BOLA TUNE DAANT DIYA
KISMAT NE NAHI MEHNAT NE MERA SAATH DIYA
MERE GAAL PE CHHAYE THE KALE BADAL
MAINE FREESTYLE KAR KE BADAL KO HI CHHAT DIYA
AUR PHIR JANTE HO USKE BAAD KYA HUA  
AUR DAB WALI CHHORI KARTI DAILY TEXT AND TEXT

MRUNAL SHANKAR
YE DIN ME INTROVERT SMALL CASE WALA UDAY 
RAAT 3 KE BAAD YE ALL CAPS WALA UDAY 
MARATHI BOLU CALL PE ISKO JANNI SAARI BAAT 
BHINBHIN KARE KAAN ME KI TRANSLATION KUTHAY!?
TERI DIL HI SE HOTI SAARI LADKIYA GAYAB HAI 
TU HUSTLE 3 KA VILLAIN HI SAHI HAI 
TOH LIKHE LOVE LETTERS APNEHI RHYME SCHEMES KO 
KYUNKI WO TERE NASEEB ME NAHI HAI

UDAY 
ISKA NAAM NHI YAAD MUJHE HAI KYU NHI AB TAK
MURNAL, MRUNIL, MERE NAAL, AH, MULI SHANKAR
ELIMINATION HO TO ROTI SABME TU
SHE'S LIKE MAI JAISE HU KOI HA-UWUWUWU
ISKA VLOG CHANNEL 18 PLUS VISIONED
KYUKI USME MAKE UP NHI HOTA, HOTI YE UNFILTERED
AUR AANSU PONCHNE KE LIYE HAI NHI SORRY TISSUES
MERI MASI KI UMAR KI YE, TO HAI BHI MOMMY ISSUES


SHADY 
JAMMU SE AAYA DEKHO SHAYAAN BHATT
GROUND SHUNYA BAAR- BAAR, PLEASE AB SHAYAAN HATT
SHAYAD SHAYAAN, SHA-YARI SHAUQEEN SHEN
SHAYAD SHABAB, SHAB-E-HIJR SHEN
POP IT, LOCK IT, DROP IT, LOCKDOWN
ROK LO, KHUD PE YAQEEN, WON'T BACK DOWN
MILA RADIO HIT, INKO MIL CHUKA THAA CROWN
PHIR AGLE HI GAANE MEIN KAR DIYA GROWL
AA - ZAA - DII
PAR KYU?

SHEN B 
NAAM SHADY HAR  KAAM ISKA LOFI
BARGAD KA PED KAISE BANEGA YEH BONZAI
BANDA LAGEY MUJHE PHEEKA YEH ZAROOR PAR ISS SE ZYADA PHEEKA THAT DROP IN HIS GENOCIDE

KAYDEN SHARMA
BURRAH PAJI AAPSE KYA KARU DEBATE? 
PICHLE HAFTE HI TOH HUE ELIMINATE CUZ
AAPKU SUPPORT KARTA PURI DELHI KA WEST SIDE
MERKU SUPPORT KARTA PURA COUNTRY KA SOUTH SIDE
GAANO ME RAKHTE KHALI 10 PERCENT RAP ISLIYE 
IHH ME AAPKU KOI MAANTA ICH NAI PHIR 
MERE JAISA COMMERCIAL BAN NE KI KOSHISH KARE LEKIN AAP KE BHAI KI BARAAT ME KOI NAACHTA ICH NAI

BURRAH 
COMMERCIAL HOTA VERSATILE TU HAI BAS BORING 
BANTA HAI TU STREET HAI PAR SIRF NACHATA HAI 
BACK TO BACK HUGTA LOWEST SCORING 
STAGE PE ROKE BABU TRP BADHATA HAI 
JAANDA MAI PUTT KINNI ATT TU KARAI
TERSE ZYADA SHOW PE FATT RE MERE BHAI
NUMBERON KI CHESS MEIN TU PYADA CHHOTE BHAI
TERE FUMBLON KI JAAN BAS VOTE NE BACHAI

RAP ID 
TRI CITY NE DIYA NI BHAVV TO PHIR BHAI TRY CITIES KARNE SEEDHE SOLAN KE PAHAAD CHAD GAYE 
PRINCE BHAI ITNE REAL RADIO HIT MILA LET‚ÄôS GO, LET‚ÄôS GO BOLA AUR SHOW SE HI BAHAR CHAL GAYE 
BHAI KI WRITING PE DOUBT KOI NAHI PAR BHAI DOCTOR HAI NA TOH BAS SAMAJH NAHI AAYI
ARRE DOCTOR SAHAB ARTHRITIS SE SEEDHA AUTHOR WRITERS KE BEECH AAP YE KAHAN HI FAS GAYE YAAR


PRINCE THE ARTIST SINGH
JIHNU KEHDA KDE BHAI OHNU DISS NAIO MARDA 
LESSGO KEHKE V MAIN WADH DEALAAN  TARDA
HAN MAIN DOCTOR KBBA JA SUBHA 
HADI TODNI TE JODNI MAIN CHNGI TRAH JAAN DA 
PUNJAB TE HIMACHAL CH KAHDI VEERE DOD AE 
LIKH DA JO GLLAN SARA JAGG KRE GAUR AE
KR DENDA ROAST JE KOI HUNDA SALA HOR AE 
LOKKAN DA TIME AANA SADDA AANA DAUR AE

VIJAY DADA 
KYA RE AMARAVATI POTA 
KRANTIKARI KHOTA 
PURA PALAT JAIGA
JAB RAKHAM RAHU MOTA 
CHAKULI MARU C SHARP TAPALI 
KHAPLI JAARE HAHAHAHA NAKILI

100RBH 
TERE CHAI NE JAGAYA NAHI TO RAHI NAHI KOI KAAM KI.
DIKHAVE KI AANDHI ASAL ME RAHETI SHANTI.
MERI TARAF DEKH DEFINATION OF A KRANTI
TU 43 KA TAAJ NAHI TU 4 DIN KI CHANDANI

GAUSH 
DEKE ZABAAN MAI
KABHI NAHI PEECHE HATA MAI
KAMINE BECHE IMAAN YE
MERE MUKAAM PE 
KABHI NAHI MILEGA DHUNDH
KABSE MERE PE KYU YE KARE SAWAAL HAI
BAATO KI NIKLE KHAAL
PAR KABHI NAHI MILE JAWAB YE 
APNA AAP MAI KARUNGA SAPNE SACH MAI
BETE TU MERE SE BACH BE

snippet.title: MEENAKSHI Full Movie | 2023 New Released Hindi Dubbed Movie | Regina Cassandra, Vennela Kishore
snippet.description:
Here's presenting "MEENAKSHI" the Hindi Dubbed Version of the Telugu action thriller mystery Film "NENE NAA", starring Regina Cassandra, Vennela Kishore, and Akshara Gowda in lead roles 

#meenakshi #nenenaa #reginacassandra 

Movie: Meenakshi  
Original Movie:- Nene Naa
Director:- Caarthick Raju 
StarCast:- Regina Cassandra, Vennela Kishore, Akshara Gowda
Presented By: RKD Studios 
Music:- Sam C.S

The film is set in two periods, the present and the 1920s. In modern times an archaeologist, as part of her job, unearths something antique which leads to mysterious events.

A foreigner is attacked and sucked into quicksand by an ethereal force. Archaeologist heroine Divya explores the situation and discovers a 120-year-old woman's skeleton. Shortly after that, the forensic reports say that the skull's facial features resemble those of Divya. Shortly after the local DSP was brutally murdered with a spear perched into him.

The forensic report identifies fingerprints on the spear that are consistent with those of a young woman. Heroine Divya tells her brother, who is assaulted by a lady who resembles her sister, about the bizarre occurrences.
 
Disclaimer:- We are only the right holders of this content. Any opinions expressed in this Film may purely be of the director or the original producers but are not our personal opinions and we do not assume any responsibility or liability for the same. 

Kindly subscribe to the channel and Press the BELL ICON to get Instant Notifications from RKD Studios.
